## No build tool required

REP works without any build tool. If you have a static HTML site with inline `<script type="module">` tags, just import the SDK from a CDN or self-hosted path:

```html
<script type="module">
  import { rep } from '/assets/rep-sdk.esm.js';
  // Use rep.get(), rep.getSecure(), etc.
</script>
```

The gateway injects the `<script id="__rep__">` payload into your HTML regardless of how your JavaScript is loaded.

